HEADWORD: Consignor
<hw>Con*sign"or</hw> <pr>(? ⟦or⟧ <?/; 277)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One
who consigns something to another; -- opposed to
<inv>consignee</inv>.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>consigner</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Consilience</ent>⟦br⟧
